{"word":"H2419 - חִיאֵל - Chîyʼêl - khee-ale' - Hiel","slug":"H2419","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חִיאֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Chîyʼêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>khee-ale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Hiel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>חיאל</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>chı̂y'êl</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>khee-ale'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Hiel = \"God lives\" <ol><li>a native of Bethel who rebuilt Jericho in the reign of Ahab and in whom was fulfilled the curse pronounced by Joshua</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H2416\">H2416</a> and <a href=\"#/H410\">H410</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2416\">H2416</a>, <a href=\"#/H2421\">H2421</a>, <a href=\"#/H2422\">H2422</a>, <a href=\"#/H2424\">H2424</a>, <a href=\"#/H2425\">H2425</a>, <a href=\"#/H3171\">H3171</a>, <a href=\"#/H3172\">H3172</a>, <a href=\"#/H3174\">H3174</a>, <a href=\"#/H4241\">H4241</a>"}]}